```plantuml
@startuml
!option handwritten true

title 迭代器模式

interface "Aggregate" as Aggregate {
    + Iterator iterator()
}

interface "Iterator" as Iterator << T >> {
    + boolean hasNext()
    + T next()
}

class "BookShelf" as BookShelf {
    + BookIterator iterator()
}

class "BookIterator" as BookIterator << Book >> {
    ~ BookShelf bookShelf
    --
    + boolean hasNext()
    + Book next()
}

Aggregate ..|> Iterator : Creates ▶

BookShelf ..|> Aggregate
BookIterator ..|> Iterator

BookShelf o-- BookIterator

note top of Aggregate : 集合，用于创建Iterator迭代器接口

note bottom of BookShelf : 会创建出具体的Iterator角色

note bottom of BookIterator : 具体的迭代器，\n包含了遍历集合所必须的信息（bookShelf）

@enduml
```
